= Admin

The administrator manages the overall system. Their responsibilities include:

- Creating and managing user accounts (students, teachers)
- Assigning roles
- Managing courses and classes
- Enrolling students
- Assigning teachers
- Viewing system statistics
- Updating platform settings

= Teacher

A teacher is responsible for:

- Managing classes
- Managing learning materials
- Managing and reviewing assignments
- Monitoring students' submissions

= Student

A student can:

- Register independently
- Log in
- View their enrolled classes
- Access learning materials
- Submit assignments
- Receive feedback
- Receive notifications
- Track their progress
